title: KFAC’s Jack-O-Lantern Jamboree slated for Oct. 29 (Morehead State University)
text: ( Source : Morehead State University ) Morehead State University's Kentucky Folk Art Center will hold a Jack-O-Lantern Jamboree at KFAC , Thursday, Oct. 29 , from 5:30 until 7:30 p.m. The evening will consist of ghost stories, music treats,
